column1: # Average monthly mean CO2 concentration for Mauna Loa and South Pole
# Monthly values have been seasonally detrended and are averaged at
# midnight on the 15th of each month
#   0 Both MLO and SPO data are real monthly averages
#   1 MLO value is filled from seasonally detrended spline fit
#  2 SPO value is filled from seasonally detrended spline fit
#  3 MLO and SPO values are filled from seasonally detrended spline fit
# CO2 concentrations are reported on the Scripps '12' calibration scale
